The second season of SPY×FAMILY. The Forger family will face a new familial mission as Yor heads on a cruise ship expedition! (Source: Crunchyroll News)
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonald’s best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maou’s plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emi’s child! (Source: Crunchyroll)

You’ve got the raw talent. Or you’re the underdog. But do you have the heart? Do you have what it takes? Let’s see what you’re made of. The real fight starts now! (Source: WEBTOONS) Note: Chapter count includes 10 special chapters, 18 side stories and 2 epilogues.

Shikimori seems like the perfect girlfriend: cute, fun to be around, sweet when she wants to be… but she has a cool dark side that comes out under the right circumstances. And her boyfriend Izumi loves to be around when that happens! (Source: Kodansha USA) Notes: - Chapter count includes 25 extra chapters. - The work was first self-published by the author on their Twitter account. - It began its official publication in Pocket Magazine on February 2, 2019. - Won 5th place in Tsugimanga 2020 Award in the Web Manga Category.
